The '''Dressian Kiolsh Merchant Bank''' was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Mygeeto/Legends|Mygeeto]] in [[Jygat]] and operated by the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan/Legends|InterGalactic Banking Clan]]. The facility was constructed below the surface, carved into Mygeeto's massive ice sheets.

During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], Sergeant [[Walon Vau]] and [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]], a Special Operations unit of [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commandos]], infiltrated the vault of Vau's father, the [[Count of Gesl]], absconding with a vast amount of riches, from precious metals and jewels, to antiques and industrial secrets.

